Class BinarySearchTreeThreaded<T extends algorithms.heapsAndPQs.HeapNode>

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.BinarySearchTreeThreaded<T>

  • public class BinarySearchTreeThreaded<T extends algorithms.heapsAndPQs.HeapNode>
extends java.lang.Object
    Building upon the BinarySearchTree by adding double threading. adapted from the following: http://adtinfo.org/libavl.html/TBST-Data-Types.html The GNU libavl 2.0.2 has the following license: http://adtinfo.org/libavl.html/Code-License.html which is GNU General Public License as published by the Free Software Foundation; either version 2. TODO: The class is not completely tested yet. Need to test more thoroughly for integrity of the bst after root node deletions.

    nichole
